name: Ha'Penny Ghouls
description:
People, like souls trapped in purgatory, move in an unmistakable pattern. Few can escape from it, many fail to understand that the path is the opposite towards the light.

Slaves to a society we don't choose, to a life we can barely cope with. Putting out the flame of the revolution, they know that we are trapped.

The greatest victory of the system is to make you believe that you cannot do anything to change it. 


Camera: OM-10
Film: Ilford fp4
